text: Moustafa Hamid Mansour (, born 8 July 1930) is an Egyptian wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Egyptian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Egypt Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Cairo
